---
import { SITE, whatsappLink } from "~/lib/config";
import type { Organization } from "~/lib/api";

interface Props {
  org: Organization | null;
}

const name = SITE.name;
const orderMessage = `Hola ${name}! Vi su web y quiero cotizar postres para una empresa, colegio o cafetería. ¿Me ayudan con opciones, cantidad, fecha y entrega?`;
---

<header class="hero-shell relative overflow-hidden pt-6 pb-20 sm:pb-28">
  <nav class="section relative z-20 flex items-center justify-between">
    <a href="#" class="group flex items-center" aria-label={`${name} - inicio`}>
      <img src="/logo-horizontal.svg" alt="El Horno del Pingüino" class="h-10 w-auto object-contain transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105" loading="eager" />
    </a>

    <div class="hidden items-center gap-7 rounded-full border border-white/70 bg-white/60 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-horno-magentaDeep/80 shadow-card backdrop-blur sm:flex">
      <a href="#catalogo" class="transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:text-horno-magenta">Catálogo</a>
      <a href="#business-heading" class="transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:text-horno-magenta">Para negocios</a>
      <a href="#contacto" class="transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:text-horno-magenta">Contacto</a>
    </div>

    <a href={whatsappLink(orderMessage)} target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-magnetic class="hidden rounded-full bg-horno-magenta px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-soft transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-horno-magentaDeep md:inline-flex">
      Cotizar para empresa
    </a>

    <button data-hamburger aria-controls="mobile-nav" class="flex min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px] flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg p-3 -mr-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-horno-magenta focus:ring-offset-2 sm:hidden" aria-label="Abrir menú" type="button">
      <span class="hamburger-line"></span>
      <span class="hamburger-line"></span>
      <span class="hamburger-line"></span>
    </button>

    <div id="mobile-nav" data-mobile-nav>
      <a href="#catalogo" class="flex min-h-[44px] items-center" tabindex="0">Catálogo</a>
      <a href="#business-heading" class="flex min-h-[44px] items-center" tabindex="0">Para negocios</a>
      <a href="#contacto" class="flex min-h-[44px] items-center" tabindex="0">Contacto</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="section relative z-10 mt-14 grid items-center gap-12 lg:mt-16 lg:grid-cols-[1.03fr_0.97fr]">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <span data-hero-anim="eyebrow" class="eyebrow rounded-full bg-white/70 px-4 py-2 shadow-card">Hechos a mano en Loja, Ecuador</span>
      <h1 data-hero-anim="heading" class="mt-4 text-4xl leading-[1.02] text-horno-magentaDeep sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        Postres artesanales para <span class="text-horno-orange">empresas, colegios y cafeterías</span>.
      </h1>
      <div data-hero-anim="accent" class="my-6 h-1.5 w-20 rounded-full bg-horno-orange" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p data-hero-anim="copy" class="mb-8 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-horno-magentaDeep/80">
        Presentación cuidada, sabor consistente y coordinación clara para reuniones, eventos, vitrinas y ocasiones especiales. Cotizamos por WhatsApp según cantidad, fecha y entrega en Loja.
      </p>

      <div data-hero-anim="actions" class="hero-actions">
        <div class="hero-actions-main">
          <a href={whatsappLink(orderMessage)} target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-magnetic class="btn-primary">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" class="h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="15" fill="#25D366" />
              <path fill="#fff" d="M16.04 7.15a8.64 8.64 0 0 0-7.38 13.12l-.93 3.43 3.51-.92a8.65 8.65 0 1 0 4.8-15.63Zm0 15.77a7.1 7.1 0 0 1-3.62-.99l-.26-.15-2.08.54.56-2.02-.17-.27a7.11 7.11 0 1 1 5.57 2.89Zm3.9-5.32c-.21-.11-1.27-.63-1.47-.7-.2-.07-.34-.11-.49.11-.14.21-.56.7-.69.84-.13.14-.25.16-.46.05-.21-.11-.9-.33-1.72-1.06-.64-.57-1.07-1.27-1.2-1.49-.13-.21-.01-.33.1-.44.1-.1.21-.25.32-.38.11-.13.14-.21.21-.36.07-.14.04-.27-.02-.38-.05-.11-.49-1.18-.67-1.62-.18-.43-.36-.37-.49-.38h-.42c-.14 0-.38.05-.58.27-.2.21-.76.74-.76 1.81s.78 2.1.89 2.25c.11.14 1.53 2.34 3.71 3.28.52.22.92.36 1.23.46.52.17.99.14 1.36.09.41-.06 1.27-.52 1.45-1.02.18-.5.18-.94.13-1.02-.05-.09-.2-.14-.41-.25Z" />
            </svg>
            Cotizar por WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a href="#catalogo" class="btn-secondary">Ver catálogo</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <ul class="mt-10 flex max-w-xl flex-col gap-3 text-sm font-medium text-horno-magentaDeep/75 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap sm:gap-x-6">
        <li data-hero-anim="badge" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-horno-magenta" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          Entrega coordinada en Loja
        </li>
        <li data-hero-anim="badge" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-horno-magenta" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          Pedidos para empresas y colegios
        </li>
        <li data-hero-anim="badge" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-horno-magenta" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          Atención directa por WhatsApp
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="relative flex min-h-[360px] items-center justify-center lg:min-h-[500px]">
      <div class="hero-card" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="hero-card-grid"></div>
        <div class="penguin-sprite" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="order-ticket order-ticket-top">Presentación cuidada</div>
        <div class="order-ticket order-ticket-bottom">Pedido coordinado</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<script>
  import "~/scripts/mobile-nav.js";
  import "~/scripts/hero-animation.js";
</script>
